GIMod¶

GIMod will solve your problem of where to start with documentation, by providing a basic explanation of how to do it easily.

Look how easy it is to use:

import GIMod # Get your stuff done GIMod.do_stuff()

Features¶

  • Be awesome
  • Make things faster

Installation¶

Install GIMod by running:

install GIMod

Contribute¶

  • Issue Tracker: github.com/GIMod/GIMod/issues
  • Source Code: github.com/GIMod/GIMod

Support¶

If you are having issues, please let us know. We have a mailing list located at: GIMod@google-groups.com
